er of voids\nis also increased in the NWs.This study will help to design CdTe NWs based\ndevices efficiently by presenting in-depth understanding of failure behavior of\nthe [111]-oriented CdTe NWs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2019 17:14:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-04"}
