isk, the important biases in\nunderdense regions call for the development of non-equilibrium methods to\nestimate the dynamical matter density locally and in the outer disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Mar 2019 02:44:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 19:29:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
